# Portafolio (edinssonmelo.com)

Before non-trivial changes, read `memory-bank/` (especially `activeContext.md`, `learnedPatterns.md`, `systemPatterns.md`).

## Must-know

- **Identity**: An AI Software Engineer (`SITE_CONFIG.tagline` in `src/config/seo.ts`)
- **Logos**: transparent PNG only. `bg-transparent` on Logo component; no background on logo `img`
- **Screenshots**: `public/screenshots/`. Never `public/projects/`
- **Deploy**: push to `main` auto-deploys via self-hosted runner on ai-server (`/srv/apps/portafolio`)
- **Style**: Cabinet Grotesk headings, DM Sans body, stone-900 navbar, lime accent `#DCFF31`
- **Design system**: `src/config/designTokens.ts` + primitives `SurfaceCard`, `SectionBadge`, `TagChip`, `Field`. Use for new UI instead of Framer `after:border` boilerplate
- **Copy**: no em dashes (`—`) in site text. Use periods, commas, colons, or parentheses. See `AGENTS.md` Copy style.

## After meaningful tasks

1. Update `memory-bank/activeContext.md` and `progress.md` with what changed.
2. **Commit and push to `main`**. Always, unless the user explicitly asks not to. **Do not ask** if they want deploy; just ship. See `AGENTS.md` for the full workflow.
